stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Open: new failure cluster<br/>SHA-256(failing fields × tool patterns)
    Open --> Resolved: candidate passes this cluster
    Resolved --> Regressed: later candidate fails it again
    Regressed --> Resolved: subsequent candidate fixes it
    Resolved --> [*]: persists across runs<br/>via run_state.json
    note right of Open
        FailureRegistry clusters cases
        by structural signature so the
        analyzer can target persistent
        failure modes — not just
        per-iteration noise.
    end note
